# When running against a local Ganache instance, you do *not* need to set contract
# addresses.  The frontend will read the address from the build artifact.  If you
# do wish to override it (for example to connect to a different network), you can
# add the following variables:
# REACT_APP_PROJECTS_CONTRACT_ADDRESS=0x...
# REACT_APP_REQUEST_MANAGER_ADDRESS=0x...